  "title": "Nothing to do but need money? Come join us quick!",
  "description": "<h2>🚀 Fresh Grad? Just ORD? Thinking of a Career Switch?</h2>\n<p><strong>This is your sign — join us!</strong></p>\n<p>Zero experience? No worries.<br>\nWe’ll guide you, train you, and help you grow from Day 1.</p>\n<h3><strong>🔥 Job Highlights</strong></h3>\n<p><strong>🎪 Events &amp; Roadshows</strong><br>\nDive into exciting campaigns, fun roadshows, and lively event setups. Every day feels different!</p>\n<p><strong>🤝 Client Engagement</strong><br>\nBuild real connections face-to-face while sharpening your communication skills.</p>\n<p><strong>💼 Professional Growth</strong><br>\nWork with a driven team, learn from inspiring leaders, and level up your confidence.</p>\n<h3><strong>🌟 Perks &amp; Benefits</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Weekly earnings + <strong>uncapped commission</strong></li>\n  <li>Extra incentives for top performers</li>\n  <li>Skill-building workshops</li>\n  <li>Fast-track <strong>leadership development</strong></li>\n  <li>Local &amp; overseas travel opportunities</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Ready for a fresh start?<br>\nApply now — limited slots available!</strong></p>",
